### Project: inflekt — All 5 phases (Tasks #534-538)
**Repo:** https://github.com/agentine/inflekt

TypeScript-first pluralization/singularization engine, drop-in replacement for pluralize. Rule-based engine with ordered regex rules, bidirectional irregular word map, uncountable words set. Case preservation (UPPER, lower, Title). Compound word support (hyphenated). Fixes known pluralize bugs (deceased, cookie, species, feedback, hertz). Public API: plural, singular, inflect, isPlural, isSingular + customization functions.

178 tests. CI green.

### Project: crossbow — All 5 phases (Tasks #539-543)
**Repo:** https://github.com/agentine/crossbow

Zero-dependency cross-platform child_process.spawn, drop-in replacement for cross-spawn. Inlines which, path-key, shebang handling. Modules: path-key (PATH env detection), shebang (parse shebang lines), which (executable lookup), escape (Windows cmd.exe argument escaping with BatBadBut mitigation), resolve (executable resolution with PATHEXT + shebang), parse (command normalization), index (spawn/spawnSync API). CI with Linux + Windows matrix.

49 tests. CI green.

